Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早餐不乖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老老实实给我待肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You go in my tummy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是第一个成功逃出来的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the first food to ever escape
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我向你致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I salute you, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个信封
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an envelope
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是很合我的口味  但也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not my favorite flavor, but whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这信封是用来开的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an opening envelope
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是用来吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not an eating envelope
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种东西应该配个说明书才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These things should come with instructions
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许海绵宝宝可以帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe SpongeBob can help
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可是样样精通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's good at stuff and things
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.81,0:02:55.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以帮我打开这个早餐信封吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:55.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you open this breakfast envelope for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也收到了早餐信封吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a breakfast envelope too?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神秘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How mysterious
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's open them together
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这信  鼻然不能开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This letter's just "snot" gonna open
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能得再使点劲才拆得开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it just needs a little extra elbow grease
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024,920)}手肘油
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.18,0:03:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd I tell--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我从前在珊瑚营地戴的领巾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My old Kamp Koral neckerchief?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我从前在珊瑚营地穿的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My old Kamp Koral underwear
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经好多年没穿过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't worn these in years
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说会不会还有谁也收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, you think anyone else got sent
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚营的欢乐回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fun Kamp Koral memories?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去问问从前的室友珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's ask our old bunkmate, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得这些回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think these memories
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我大脑供血不足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are cutting off the circulation to my brain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信封
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Envelope?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  确实有收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I got one of those
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一打开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Opened it up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.76,0:04:05.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前戴过的牙套就飞进了我嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and got hit right in the kisser by my old braces
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  大家都收到奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool, everyone got a prize
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真相大白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, mystery solved
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们没看过信封里的信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you read the letter in the envelope?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The letter?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怀念小时候无忧无虑的日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Do you miss the carefree days of your youth?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用再烦恼了  我特地邀请你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Well, pine away no more, because you're invited
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来珊瑚营地参加超棒团圆会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"to a killer reunion at Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来重温童年  一起狂欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Come relive your childhood and party down
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证可以嗨死你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll just die from all the fun"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,署名  X
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Signed "X"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道这个是什么意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.38,0:04:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个  指的就是特定的人或物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"This" refers to a specific person or object
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是这么个事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that is right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但意思也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it also means
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要重返珊瑚营地了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're going back to Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击掌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High five
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击掌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High five
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(288,384)}贻贝海滩
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,练出肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get swole
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meep?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meep?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.08,0:05:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moop?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.25,0:05:14.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:14.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mop
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't going
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回我从前办的夏令营开破烂团圆会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to some dumb reunion at me old summer camp
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好不容易及时把那破地方关了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I barely shut that place down in time
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才避免违反各种卫生法令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to avoid all those health code violations
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个半毛钱硬币我到哪都认得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd know this nickel anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,附注  眼熟不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"P.S. Look familiar?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有胆的话  就来找剩下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come and get the rest if you dare"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有地图  能带我找失踪的营地硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A map to me lost camp nickels
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藏得特别深  连我都忘记放哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ones I hid so well, even I forgot where I hid ‘em
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟钱要团圆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and me money
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这团圆会倒是值得一去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's a reunion worth attending
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.38,0:06:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  等不及要重返珊瑚营地了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I can't wait to go back to Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是没错  可要怎么过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but how are we gonna get there?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我独轮车拿去卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My unicycle's in the shop
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.76,0:06:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.09,0:06:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以蹦蹦跳跳过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could prance
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好久没蹦蹦跳跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't pranced in ages
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上大巴就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just get on the bus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  大巴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, the bus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实坐大巴更合理些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do suppose that makes sense
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:29.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1228,458)}您正在\N驶出裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等我  兄弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, dudes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此企鹅男孩  用了双手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's why Barnacle Boy, with both hands
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哞哞哞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moop moop moop
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看什么看  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at, boy-o?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自打夏令营你就没变过  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit since camp, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位营友们好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, fellow campers
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想亲自感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to personally thank
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邀请我们参加盛大团圆会的营友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,whoever invited us to the big reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So who was it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到了营地就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sure to know when we get there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.79,0:07:26.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一站  赚钱营地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:26.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next stop, Kamp Money
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是那个珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good old Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1214,690)}珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,莫名感觉有些不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It seems different somehow
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.41,0:07:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里好像改名叫册吕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like they changed the name to Ka-Ka
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:59.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,792)}册             吕
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不说  这里真的荒废了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I must say, the place has really gone to pot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I think someone
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在借团圆会的名头耍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is pulling a fast one with this reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别听她的  小硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to her, little nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就能找到你朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll find your friends soon
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.68,0:08:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱就是说  这地方比我记忆中小多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is, like, way smaller than I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是地方小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not smaller
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just bigger
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是地方确实烂了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it is a lot crummier
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  玩笑开得已经够过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I think this joke has gone far enough
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家回大巴上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone, back on the bus
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们绝不留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are not staying here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not to worry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去拿修理工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get the tools
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把轮胎装回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we'll put the wheels back on
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could just--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来得步行过桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like we're walking back across the bridge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只好走老旧隧道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have to use the old tunnel
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's OK
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到热气球场去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the hot air balloon field
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被困了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trapped
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有出路都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every way to get is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被困的怕是只有你们贱民才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe for the likes of you rabble
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.79,0:09:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞吉吉尔德  执行救富行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Regigilled, commence Operation Wealth Extraction
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.01,0:09:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  瑞吉吉尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Regigilled
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.73,0:09:49.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你们把我第三爱的直升机怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:49.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what you've done to my third-favorite helicopter
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒犯到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am offended
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码没有谁受伤  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least no one got hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:02.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686,334)}营长
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于只有自己一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally alone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来找找我的财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to find me booty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看  向南一百步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, 100 paces south
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我让开  小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of my way, cabin
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid cabin
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四五
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,4, 5
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下该怎么办  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should we do now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁看到尤金了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen Eugene?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I saw him
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胳膊底下夹着个东西走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,walk off with something under his arm
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.15,0:10:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爸要是胳膊夹着报纸就走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If my dad had a newspaper under his arm when he left
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定好几个小时都不见踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we won't see him for a couple of hours
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九十八
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,98
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.28,0:10:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九十九
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,99
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,100
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叉叉表示藏宝地点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,X marks the spot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Found it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来取走里面的财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to get what's coming to me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那声音听起来像蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds like Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,having a blast
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板不愧是营长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good ol' Camp Master Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太会玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He knows how to have fun
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能还有一趟接我们回去的大巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's another bus to take us home
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海加护士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nurse Helga
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来开团圆会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am here for the reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错过什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd I miss?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.33,0:11:36.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子我来得刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:36.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it looks like I got here just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来  受伤的小胖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back, bubby with the boo-boo
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来珊瑚营地重新开张了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like Kamp Koral is reopen for business
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙们  如果非得困在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, gang, if we're gonna be stuck here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒不如来享受下重返营地的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we might as well enjoy being back in camp
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蹦跳欢呼往日珊瑚营
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump up and cheer for old Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,570)}珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食物做工差  味道不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where the food is bad and tastes abnormal
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,床上到处都是虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bunks are filled with bugs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树林也很不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the woods are paranormal
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们热爱珊瑚营
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we love it here in camp
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以肯定不会吵吵嚷嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So there'll be no quarrel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱这都快没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna die out here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's happening
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.34,0:12:19.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这真是我们从前的小屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:19.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this really our old cabin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:28.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1356,180)}游艇
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞吉吉尔德  开门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Regigilled, door
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如您所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, heavens
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无法容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outrageous
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们美丽的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our beautiful cabin's
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来还是豪宅  现在变破棚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gone from chateau to shanty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞吉吉尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Regigilled
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如您所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.75,0:13:00.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西的疙瘩比我记忆中还要多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:00.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a bit lumpier than I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is haunted
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞吉吉尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Regigilled
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如您所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可否还有其他吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will there be anything else?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如您所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮忙移走直升机那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for removing that helicopter thingy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可现在我肚子又空洞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But now my stomach is empty again
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imbeciles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.75,0:13:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这小屋临走时本来还很干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This cabin was spotless when I left
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的手术刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My scalpels
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的夹钳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My clamps
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的劈砍工具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My slashing tools
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All gone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.52,0:13:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does someone have a boo-boo?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.31,0:14:02.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要海加护士治好你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:02.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you need Nurse Helga to put you back together?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you please keep it down
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那声很明显是狼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was obviously a werewolf
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可现在才白天  压根没月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's daytime, and there's no moon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就肯定是有个到处抢劫的营地怪客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then it must be some sort of marauding camp creeper
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个更严重的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have bigger problems
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滑索上面没吊具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It appears there's no mechanism for zipping
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就随机应变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then let's improvise
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.33,0:14:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我屁股连续两次摔出脑震荡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My posterior has suffered
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a double cranial concussion
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子好像不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not looking so good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他屁股受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His butt is wiped out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你了  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.59,0:15:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我屁股不至于难看成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure my butt doesn't look that bad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Kevin?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文  别鬼混了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin, quit goofing around
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a feeling
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.48,0:15:28.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这附近发生了超自然现象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:28.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's something supernatural going on around here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a feeling too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屁股不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in my glutes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.25,0:15:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.92,0:15:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snacks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.04,0:15:45.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:45.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snacks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板餐车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Kanteen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.60,0:16:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别骂我没尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:16:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let no man say I didn't try
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁在冲我吐水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is someone blorping at me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.19,0:16:13.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再非法倾倒一桶过期海霸糊就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just one more drum
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:13.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of expired chum left to illegally dump
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不懂你为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持要大老远过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,insisted on coming all the way out here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只为了倒点海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just to dump some chum
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为就连白痴都不会大老远过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because not even an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would come all the way out here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是来开派对狂欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here for the party
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.59,0:16:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没收到珊瑚营地团圆会邀请吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you get an invite to the Kamp Koral reunion?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,团圆会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reunion?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.56,0:16:44.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我凭什么要去那什么破烂托儿会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:44.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would I go to a dumb daycare reunion?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,‘Cause we're getting hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先前在这当过大厨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you were the cook here once
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我去下厨  大厨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So why don't you get cooking, cook?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大厨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cook?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非拿你脸下厨不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll cook your face
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先别急
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy, Tiger
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.33,0:17:05.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配合一下  省得被他们举报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:05.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's play along so they don't report us
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come and get it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lousy punks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该不会真要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not really gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他们吃这种腐烂海霸糊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,feed them this putrid chum, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,污染营友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Polluting campers
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.39,0:17:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总比污染湖水更环保吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is more environmentally conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than polluting the lake
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  面条呆脑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, noodle brain?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呆脑面条
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brain noodles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我突然就不饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, I'm not hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me neither
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想打排球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does anybody want to play some volleyball?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does a one-legged duck swim in circles?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meep
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meep
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玷污到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been sullied
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a shower
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.28,0:18:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't shower
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就没看过恐怖片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you never seen a horror movie?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪客会抓走你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Creeper will get you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我落单了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm alone
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.92,0:18:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一样也违反了恐怖片的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's against the horror movie rules too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meep, meep, meep
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meep, meep, meep
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meep
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:00.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,174)}淋浴
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这块我向来都刷不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can never get back there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈维  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harvey, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好干净
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So clean--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.11,0:19:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干净得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so terrifyingly clean
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好干净
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So clean
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受困的这个营地脏乱差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While we're stuck at this dirty camp
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,排球冠军会花落谁家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who's gonna be the volleyball champ?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各就位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这次发球叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call this serve the
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.40,0:20:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  可不可以请你把球还回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hey, Mister, can we get our ball back, please?"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,局面会很小气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's gotta stingy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往回打
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit 'em back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狠狠暴击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whack attack
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小船队加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dinghies
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来捡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耍小聪明是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wise guy, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you laughing at?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之所以笑  是因为树林在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just laughing because the woods are laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿莫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Mo?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很明显是被我烧到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Obviously, incinerated by me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该是想说吓到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you mean "intimidated"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还是要摧毁你  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're still gonna destroy you, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高个  你来替补
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tall Tail, you're subbed in
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.71,0:21:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点啊  高个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tall Tail
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,努力加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pull up your socks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打到球  胜利得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smash that ball, win it all
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,体育一定行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go Jocks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.00,0:21:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这次发球叫  深度撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call this serve Deep Impact
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,勉强打中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barely hit me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.53,0:21:42.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:42.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住游艇小屋的那几个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Yacht Cabin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海加护士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nurse Helga
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凤尾鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Anchovies
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.21,0:22:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连体育健将也都神秘消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now the jocks have all mysteriously disappeared
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.59,0:22:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半是到哪个地方去玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're probably just somewhere having fun
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半是入土了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in their graves
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定有个非常像样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's a perfectly good
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.73,0:22:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合情合理  有科学依据的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,highly reasonable
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,scientifically-proven explanation
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.52,0:22:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能说明他们为什么消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for their disappearances
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.98,0:22:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况体育健将又没有全都不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And besides, not all the jocks are gone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.07,0:22:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高个还
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tall Tail is still--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.40,0:22:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,jumping flapjacks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.74,0:22:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚营怪客又下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Kamp Creeper strikes again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.95,0:22:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,团圆会不有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This reunion's not so fun
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.50,0:22:39.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个中招的向来都是啦啦队员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:39.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The cheerleaders always the next one
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个哭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a C-R-Y
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:48.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,788)}未完待续
